&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#augmentedreality<\/a> projects is now a quick copy-paste job. Read more here: <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/HO6fVH1UsZ\">https:\/\/t.co\/HO6fVH1UsZ<\/a> <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/Emw7vlAFdV\">pic.twitter.com\/Emw7vlAFdV<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u2014 Overly app (@OverlyApp) <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/OverlyApp\/status\/1523951637592739841?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 10, 2022<\/a><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>The team took their inspiration from their collaboration project with world-renowned street artist, KIWIE. Together, they built a system where scanned geotags would result in a partnered NFT data arriving from the Rarible marketplace in all its AR glory.<\/p>\n<p>Following this, Overly developed their systems to automatically <strong>pull NFT data<\/strong> from the OpenSea platform. However, users can still display items hosted on alternative marketplaces by uploading a copy of the image.<\/p>\n<p>What\u2019s more, Overly offers a 5 day, no credit card required, trial of its system. So users can jump in and give it a go without spending a penny.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Try out Overly for free &gt;&gt; <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/overlyapp.com\/\">Here<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><b>Want more? Connect with NFT Plazas<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/mailchi.mp\/ecadf05eb1bf\/1\">Join the Weekly Newsletter<br \/><\/a><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/discord.gg\/qSQwMaM\">Join our Discord<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/nftplazas\">Follow us on Twitter<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/nftplazas\">Like us on Facebook<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\